title: Dungeon's Barrage
notes: Doesn't even show Unity graphics select menu screen, crashes immediately.
specs: Intel Pentium N3540 / Intel HD Graphics

gpu: Intel Open Source Technology Center Mesa DRI Intel(R) Bay Trail x86/MMX/SSE2
notes: Put "PROTON_USE_WINED3D11=1 %command%" in the launch settings of the game. After that, it works perfectly with no noticable performance drops.
